{"type": "article", "id": 24599, "title": "这个设计了不起之今日最佳", "description": "我们尝试推荐一些最近发现的聪明设计。好设计并不只是一种装饰，它还是人们对于生活细节的各种思考，并且综合了包括技术、商业在内的多种力量。我们希望持续关注这些变化，它是美好生活的动力之一。", "date": "2016-03-29T06:59:20Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 1954, "name": "包装"}, {"id": 248, "name": "COS"}, {"id": 2629, "name": "HAY"}, {"id": 16270, "name": "Industrial Facility"}, {"id": 25515, "name": "Carity"}, {"id": 25516, "name": "BLOCD."}, {"id": 25517, "name": "Kim Markel"}, {"id": 25518, "name": "MDT-tex"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 47, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607174259BMN95xDp6nH3WE1s.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p>\n<h2>2016 春季家居 by COS &amp; HAY </h2>\n<p>丹麦品牌 HAY 和时尚品牌 COS 有多次合作和联合门店，这是他们新推出的 2016 春季家居系列。将一些 HAY 原有的配件设计放在绿、蓝、粉这三种更加活泼明快的颜色中，可以组成系列。COS 的设计师 Martin Andersson 称“我们想要让 HAY 的东西有 COS 的感觉”。这些产品目前可以在 COS 的门店和网站上找到，<a href=\"http://www.cosstores.com/gb/COSxHAY/All\">这里是购买链接</a>。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607111856AaH4DYhsJ78BxlPg.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607111856fA9UCIODHJlYaSdB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.98397436\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607111857lJ0EiIH8jXdCQW7R.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607111858kXMGA2OCuNPscVob.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71481481\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607111858D5dGoh8WJFuLga4k.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66111111\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607111859hvwekFuoObdL0qi2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.60833333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>Ode lamps by Industrial Facility </h2>\n<p>这组灯来自伦敦设计工作室 Industrial Facility ，它有一个像蘑菇一样的圆盘形灯罩，灯罩下面是极细的长灯柱，两者间构成了对比和反差，也让这盏灯体现出了极简和轻盈的美感。设计师认为这就是街上常见的灯，它包括落地灯、台灯和与桌子相连的灯。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607111859rj92usOUVo8zlRax.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607111900JysAZu8BQecvwIgE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607111900JLmrnlwQsNKPgcyt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071119019rWAQlw8ajBpY6kM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607111901tQDiH1pXqgz6CuNo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.25\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>glow furniture by Kim Markel</h2>\n<p>这组家具带给人童话的梦幻，纽约的女设计师 Kim Markel 使用再生塑料和树脂制作这些桌椅、镜子、花瓶等生活用品，它们结构简单而色彩单一，保留了打磨后的手工感，材料本身呈现出的半透明也令人想起一些甜品。镜子和花瓶可出售，其中像棒棒糖一样的镜子售价 120 美元，<a href=\"http://www.kimmarkel.com/shop/\">这里是购买链接。</a></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607111902Cn4K5RAEJsqV0zd3.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607111902orVkRHtLiZcXEA98.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607111903IwMkruDUQtj8E1B2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.99666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607111903lHTzuFB0DWrGmV4Q.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071119034tprT1J32vyLBIMG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>Tulip Umbrella by MDT-tex </h2>\n<p>这把用于户外的伞是一个倒三角，像一个打开的郁金香，因为打开的面积很大且接近水平，它依然有挡雨和遮阳的功能，也带有一些未来感。雨水是顺着中间的柱子往地下流的，有助于集中排水。它是用铝结构和有一定防水效果的面料制成，可承担 60 km/h 的风速和 350 mm 水压。可以选择 11 种颜色来适应各种气氛，<a href=\"https://www.mdt-tex.com/en/products/tulip-umbrella/type-e/\">这里是购买链接。</a></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607111904ZHYPUnT69GEhsl8b.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.64550781\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071119048cUe4nKalXTNdM0I.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.640625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071119054DJviaRNfQEX6Bxt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.76433121\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607111906wEiBkYF7TxHo2Qyg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071119063TmEFzaVJwrRMpWg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071119076RDKyuvpCXf4qkcY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>Carity by Carity</h2>\n<p>来自旧金山的设计工作室 Carity 发明了一个同名的空气净化器。将风扇安装在花盆上，就可以将净化后的空气排出了。花盆中内置 WiFi 模块可以及时将信息发送到智能手机的软件上，监测空气质量和湿度，并控制风扇的转速。产品目前正在众筹，<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/628579643/clairy-the-most-amazing-natural-air-purifier?ref=project_link\">这里是众筹链接</a>。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071119072pDYPVRxc1NHA9OF.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071119088QomYPwNS2xZeCpg.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.73594132\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607111909Q9aEP4tikhZTRXSu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.73594132\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607111909JoPV1sXY0EIh42gi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.73594132\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"></div>\n<h2>Chocolate Pantone by BLOCD.</h2>\n<p>这组巧克力包装有色票的感觉，打开盒子后从白色到黑色一共 6 块巧克力，中间是浅棕色到深棕色的过渡，简洁而有辨识度。每一块巧克力上面不忘写下对应的色号说明，很形象。西班牙平面设计公司 BLOCD. 想要设计圣诞节的礼品以送给客户，他们认为色票最能象征视觉设计。<a href=\"http://blocd.com/work/chocolate-pantone/\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016060711191019xchIyaAlLNQRpt.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071119109pD3esgxLIQ0XTm2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607111911W0QYMrg2DvHfJqbe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607111911H3lGbOyCV2U9hzWQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n\n"}